\f0\b \cf0 3. "The 'I Am' Activation"
\f1\b0 \cell 
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 1. Stand or sit with a straight spine. \
\
2. Place a hand on your heart. \
\
3. Speak the following decree aloud with intention: "I AM the Light. I AM the Love. I AM the Power. I AM." \
\
4. Repeat 3 or 7 times, feeling the vibration of the words in your chest and body. \
\
5. Feel the energetic shift in your field.\cell 
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Used to activate and affirm one's personal sovereignty and divine identity. Recommended for moments of self-doubt or fear.\cell 
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 "Say it as a decree, a statement of fact, not a wish. Feel the truth of it."\cell 
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 "Power of I Am" (YouTube, 2020) @ 15:00\cell 
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

